{
  "stem": "16790.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had 10 marks, which was about $4.20.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We could leave with that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we left a lot of things behind, including our maid and governess.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I remember we left in the evening and went to the train station.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we boarded this, this train to go to Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we got there the next day early in the morning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother got us into this hotel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, you got to realize that most, most hotels would not take Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But my mother knew of a commercial hotel, like a businessman's hotel, where she could go because they knew my father there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they allowed us to stay there one night until we could get on the so that we could-- we could leave them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, didn't feel safe on the train because we were still in Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no rowdyism.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there was a, a tremendous amount of apprehension because we didn't know if we were getting-- if we were going to get on this ship to leave.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were quite concerned about that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother was very much concerned, my grandmother, also.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, both of them were very apprehensive and very-- it was a very stressful time for both-- for, for both those two ladies, as well as for my sister and myself.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we felt very much estranged from the whole world, except for our, our closest immediate relatives.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Do you remember the name of the hotel, by the way?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know it was somewhere on the docks, close to the docks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it wasn't a very nice hotel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I remember my mother told me not to take off my clothes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to-- we had to sleep with our clothes on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] How's it going?",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
